{"tid":1405520,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港因為黑警其實巳經獨立成國，叫「黑港共和國」","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T10:14:39.000Z","uid":261343,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2d86c8260d759367c256c6faa9043ef9ac030516","tid":1405520,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:06:08.000Z","msg":"點解咁講？<br />\n<br />\n除左皇帝既軍隊之外，跟本唔會有人係可以免除問責。即使係林奠都要聽中央既指示。<br />\n<br />\n不過「一哥皇帝」同佢既「黑幫軍團」就唔同，佢地跟本不受監察，中意點做就點做，呢家既「黑兵」永遠唔會因為做錯事而受到懲罰，就連中央、特首同政務司司長都唔敢出聲得罪佢地，可想而知佢地既勢力係幾咁強大。一哥跟本係自擁軍隊，自立為皇，差在未講出口。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地為左奪回香港作為國家既主權，我地要建立服務人民既軍隊，「香革義兵」，討伐黑警既皇權，以正義之師，搶回香港主權。"},{"pid":"86499be3caa34d1e0c51c30a93fd7df8d4624f6c","tid":1405520,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:06:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4848947ca7c1a0838f1c5389c2f99d4b852f5d","tid":1405520,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:07:19.000Z","msg":"諗諗下唔應該係共和國，應該直接叫黑港國"},{"pid":"80c8c49d4adb5f9fc7418d71cfaad3d132e53e07","tid":1405520,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:07:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好多人都因為各種原因<br />\n唔能夠85罷工<br />\n佢地絕對需要<span style=\"color: red;\">被罷工</span><br />\n佢地都好為香港出一分力<br />\n各位連登仔/港鐵站車長站長<br />\n請幫幫手<br />\n<br />\n致各司機<br />\n堵塞各個主要交通幹道<br />\n屯門公路/大欖隧道/青馬大橋/獅子山隧道/大老山隧道/觀塘迴旋處/紅隧等等<br />\n各式各樣<span style=\"color: red;\">交通意外</span><br />\n請各位司機配合<br />\n真正全民大罷工！<br />\n8月5日香港需要你<br />\n<br />\n致港鐵車長站長<br />\n大圍/九龍塘/紅磡/調景嶺/金鐘/旺角/西鐵<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5:00</span>開始全民不合作運動<br />\n各連登仔幫忙<span style=\"color: red;\">接力</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用最少資源做到最大效益<br />\n港鐵快跑運動<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">急停制/路軌/車長室/火警鐘撳手</span>等等<br />\n分3/4 team人可癱瘓一個上午</span><br />\n港鐵車長/站長可<span style=\"color: red;\">按章工作</span><br />\n幫幫忙盡量拖延時間<br />\n香港人需要你</span>"},{"pid":"b8429dff9349fc6243503ddeff596213a2016b6f","tid":1405520,"uid":269934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:13:41.000Z","msg":"支持張建宗！<br />\n<br />\n佐級協會以下犯上，冇大冇細，根本就係想攬權成立軍政府！林鄭已經消失左10幾日，而家邊個話事顯而易見😡"},{"pid":"22a83a3edc7818050a7a8cbcd0c22870dd7078d3","tid":1405520,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"時代革命<br />\n奪回香港主權"},{"pid":"ece0a8323deeac9704f7e294719d76877da00e23","tid":1405520,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"觀察到新戰術：四散游擊，街坊落場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"52f5379445b27b4c48890cf4057f106e348c8866","tid":1405520,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0de228f46e24866690f9388346fefbfe1db4c49","tid":1405520,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:22:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1405338/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[804] 係堅尼地城/西環有需要落腳嘅手足入黎!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5f7435b25dbdcaee920aee5546ce62f1f8af43","tid":1405520,"uid":261343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T13:29:43.000Z","msg":"有無更好既義士統稱？<br />\n